node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou A Big Mac doesn't cost $3.99, it costs your health. Netflix doesn't cost $17.99, it costs your time. Social Media isn't free, it costs your focus. Lesson:'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 30, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou There is always a hidden cost. Always ask yourself what's more expensive? Buying a healthy meal for $10 or paying a medical bill after having a stroke? Paying for a useful education once or dying full of regrets?'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 30, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou The most expensive things are not the ones with the biggest price tag. It's the things you don't do that come back to bite you. Want proof?'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 30, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou Imagine you don't invest in learning how to make a million dollars. You might save yourself a few grand but every year you don't make a million.... You pay the difference for your ignorance. Here's an example:'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 30, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Basha J Katou @basharjkatou Let's say you make $50,000/ year. Every year you don't make a million, it's costing your $950,000 Because you coulo have made that- you just didn't know how to.'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 30, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou So be wise what opportunities you pass on- It might be the biggest regret of your life! Always invest in yourself!'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 30, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou Now, look at your dreams and goals... And don't ask if you can ever afford them. Ask if you can afford NOT to Invest in yourself!'.

Photo by Business Blurb™ on August 30, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou If your current lifestyle can't finance them... How will this ever change if you do nothing? So don't let your dreams die and wither just because you wanted to save a few dollars.'.

Photo shared by Business Blurb™ on August 30, 2021 tagging @basharjkatou. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Bashar J Katou @basharjkatou Take action and do something about your goals NOW. If you don't know how to start- follow my page @basharjkatou, it's gonna give you a few pointers on where to go. And now go get it!'.
